00:21.291 --> 00:22.917
This Spotz app is genius.

00:23.000 --> 00:26.291
I mean,
Airbnb for your driveway.

00:26.375 --> 00:28.500
How many times have I looked
at my driveway and thought,

00:28.583 --> 00:30.208
"How can I make money
off of you?"

00:30.291 --> 00:31.625
Not once, you know,

00:31.709 --> 00:33.667
which is why I didn't think
of this.

00:33.750 --> 00:35.166
Well, thinking of apps

00:35.250 --> 00:37.417
and standing to pee

00:35.250 --> 00:37.417
is a young man's game.

00:37.500 --> 00:40.250
Okay. Well,

00:37.500 --> 00:40.250
I'll write that down.

00:40.333 --> 00:41.417
Greg, meet the team.

00:41.500 --> 00:43.500
This is Austin.

00:41.500 --> 00:43.500
You probably know her

00:43.583 --> 00:45.375
from her gamertag,

00:43.583 --> 00:45.375
PookieGunner.

00:45.458 --> 00:46.458
'Sup?

00:46.542 --> 00:49.000
Sandy, aka BedBathAndBeyoncé.

00:49.083 --> 00:50.041
